{
  "name": {
    "en": "Tomate",
    "zh": "番茄"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": "A savory cocktail featuring tomato juice, gin, and a hint of heat. Refreshing and perfect for brunch.",
    "zh": "一款美味的雞尾酒，以番茄汁、琴酒和一絲辛辣味為特色。 清爽，非常適合早午餐。"
  },
  "historical_reference": {
    "en": "The Tomate is a variation of the Bloody Mary, replacing vodka with gin. The exact origin is not clearly documented, but it likely emerged as bartenders experimented with different spirits in the classic Bloody Mary recipe. The Tomate likely originated in the mid-20th century.",
    "zh": "Tomate 是血腥瑪麗的一種變體，用琴酒代替伏特加。 確切的起源沒有明確的記錄，但它很可能是調酒師在經典的血腥瑪麗食譜中嘗試不同的烈酒而出現的。 Tomate 可能起源於 20 世紀中葉。"
  },
  "technique": {
    "en": "Combine all ingredients in a shaker with ice. Shake well and strain into a glass filled with ice.",
    "zh": "將所有成分與冰塊放入搖酒器中。 充分搖晃並濾入裝滿冰塊的玻璃杯中。"
  },
  "garnish": {
    "en": "Cherry tomato or celery stalk",
    "zh": "小番茄或芹菜莖"
  },
  "serve_in_glass": {
